  }), mdx("p", null, "If you are developing an application that require to have money, they are big change that this money must be in a currency. So, every time you have to select a money, you have to select the currency too. A design pattern is to have a class that represent the money instead of using a decimal directly."), mdx("p", null, "For example."), mdx("pre", null, mdx("code", {
